metadata.name: Le Voyageur
metadata.description:
Break the rules. take the red pill. don't be afraid to dream. dream big. and follow your path. just like this traveler. "Le Voyageur" en Français.

First token under the "Archives collection" smart contract minted on manifold and available only on SuperRare. October 25th 2022.

The Primary Sale includes a Museum Quality Print of the Artwork (on canvas) which will be delivered to the first buyer. Size: 60x42cm.
